# Naming Conventions

| Target | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Files & folders | kebab-case | `user-profile.tsx`, `auth-utils/` |
| Components, Types, Classes, Global Objects | PascalCase | `UserCard`, `AuthService`, `ApiConfig` |
| Variables, instances, functions | camelCase | `userName`, `fetchUser()` |
| Global constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `MAX_RETRIES`, `API_BASE_URL` |

```ts
// ❌
const API_url = 'https://...'
const UserName = 'Alice'
const FETCH_user = () => {}

// ✅
const API_BASE_URL = 'https://...'
const userName = 'Alice'
const fetchUser = () => {}
type UserProfile = { name: string }
```
